<i>adverb</i>: 빙그레 [빙그레] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>빙그레 [빙그레]</dt><br>
<dd>smilingly; beamingly</dd><br>
<dd>입을 조금 벌리거나 입가를 약간 올리고 소리 없이 웃는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of smiling quietly with one's mouth slightly open or the corners of one's mouth slightly lifted.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>